data.description: This enchanting home sits on elevation 1000 feet nestled aside the majestic west Maui Mountains. Wailuku Heights, a coveted neighborhood. Breathtaking views of the ocean, harbor, and Haleakala. A beautiful, custom, two-story Family Home to love in and live in. This central Maui location makes living as a professional or a family convenient, carefree, and fun. Granite and marble throughout the upper floors, tiled on the first floor. Swaggering chandelier, new appliances, two car garage, central vacuum, central AC, 300-degree catwalk with gorgeous views of the north shore, Kahului harbor and Haleakala.
